        <h3 class="title subsection-title dark-indigo">Cost savings</h3>
        <p class="muted">Administrative tasks such as manually entering data into your system, which in turn was received by letter, fax, or email, belongs to the past. With the blockchain technology of LTO Network, all parties can collect structured data into the systems they use to execute and administer these processes. By doing so, LTO Network reduces the administrative overhead with more than 30%.</p>
